verbose_text: These LDH nanosheets with a large abundance of oxygen vacancies that enhanced the adsorption and activation of N 2 with excellent photocatalytic activity in transforming N 2 to NH 3 under UV-vis excitation and in some selected cases visible excitation (CuCr-NS under wavelength> 500 nm).
